      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction; Dec 28, 2006, obituary of former Pres Gerald R Ford misstated his relationship to three brothers; they were his half-brothers, not stepbrothers; Dec 30, 2006, article misstated year Ford moved to Palm Desert, Calif; it was 1977</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Film entry on Sunday in the Week Ahead report of Arts &amp; Leisure about a Robert Altman retrospective gave an incorrect address and phone number for the theater, IFC Center. It is at 323 Avenue of the Americas, at West Third Street, Greenwich Village -- not at 209 West Houston Street, South Village. The number is (212) 924-7771.</p>
      </block>
